    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A geometrical figure comprising the set of all points in three-dimensional space lying the same distance (the radius) from a given point (the center), or the result of rotating a circle about one of its diameters.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
